	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>&#44; <date>Mai 13th 1867</date></p>
				<p>Dear Sir&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">my friend <persName>Mr. N. Gotthelf</persName> of <placeName>Washington</placeName>&#8212;<lb/>recommended me to you.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><del>I am</del> I come from <placeName>Seligenstadt</placeName> <add>&#63;</add><lb/> <add>&#63;</add>.  My son who works here as a<lb/> bookkeeper&#44; as well as his boss&#44; a <persName>Mr. Selidenberg</persName><lb/> asked me to come here to act as a cantor and<lb/> teacher for the P<add>&#63;</add> school.  I came <del>to</del> with my<lb/> wife and three children but came <sic>to</sic> late and the job<lb/> had been given to someone else although the president<lb/> of the congregation knew about it&#59; that is my start<lb/> in <placeName>America</placeName>.  &#8220;All beginnings are hard&#8221; <add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I know my job and was even a<lb/> preacher and was greatly acknowledged.  I now<lb/> ask you to help me find <del>if</del> a <del>n honorable</del><lb/> dignified job&#44; if that is possible for you.  A<lb/> job which is worthy of a gentleman&#44; skilled in<lb/> learning <add>Hebrew</add> liberal <del>free</del> religion&#44; according to the laws of <persName>Moses</persName> and of <placeName>Israel</placeName>&#8212;<add>Hebrew</add><lb/> I can bring excellent character and <add>&#63;</add> references<lb/> as well as written testimonials showing that<lb/> I <del>am 30</del> have been in the service of Un.<lb/> .... for 30 years. &#8220;A wise man will understand&#8221;<lb/> <add>Hebrew</add></p>
			<pb n="2R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)">2</p>
				<p>I am looking forward to your reply and<lb/> am yours very truly</p>
			<p>&#40;<persName role="author">Samuel</persName>&#41; <hi rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">S. Kuttnauer</persName></hi></p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><placeName>S. Bond St. 200</placeName></p>
		</body>
